overview: The very best of Jon Moxley's time in Combat Zone Wrestling.  Matches include: Jon Moxley vs. Jon Dahmer Switchblade Conspiracy vs. Brain Damage & Drake Younger Jon Moxley vs. Brain Damage Dining Room Deathmatch: Jon Moxley vs. Brain Damage Fans Bring the Weapons: Jon Moxley vs. Nick Gage vs. Scotty Vortekz Switchblade Conspiracy vs. Danny Havoc & Necro Butcher Jon Moxley vs. Sami Callihan Ultraviolent Rules: Jon Moxley vs. Drake Younger vs. Nick Gage No Rope Barbed Wire: Jon Moxley vs. Nick Gage Jon Moxley vs. Homicide Jon Moxley vs. Jake Crist  Plus many more, in this 9 hour presentation.
title: CZW: Explicitly Moxley
